Habitat notes: All specimens of the type series were collected in small shallow temporary pools within the forest, about 0.5 –2.0 m of diameter, and about 15 cm deep (
Fig. 6
). The water was turbid and the bottom was litter. No other fish was found in these pools, which were almost contiguous to a lagoon, where no specimen of the new species was found.
